Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na COVID-19 y'abantu benshi cyane, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, yatumye habaho icyorezo cya mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi gihita gisakara mu bindi bihugu, kirimo icyorezo cy'indwara n'ubwandu.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya COVID-19 mu mateka ya vuba y'abantu.
Nkuko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1.1, ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa (NHC) yabonye ko mu Bushinwa havumbuwe amoko ya mbere y'indwara ya PNM ifite inkomoko itazwi.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, icyemezo cyo gutanga COVID cyatanzwe.
Ku wa 15 Mutarama 2020, ni bwo habonetse icyorezo cya mbere cy'abantu bahitanywe n'ibiza mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu migi, intara n'ibihugu by'abaturanyi.
Ku wa 20 Mutarama, abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi bagaragaje ko banduye, bagaragaza ko bashobora guhitana abantu.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, hakurikiyeho Guma mu rugo, kandi imihanda yose ikora imodoka yahagaritswe.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere mu by'ubuvuzi bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bari bamaze kwandura indwara, 21 gusa ari bo bagiranye na Wuhan Seafood Market, aho bahise babona ko ari ho hatangiriraga kwandura indwara ziturutse ku nyamaswa zitamenyekanye.
Ku wa 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo ari imimerere y'ubukungu ku isi.
Kugeza ubwo iyi raporo yasohokaga, icyo cyorezo cyari kimaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi (Igishushanyo 2.2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka mu buryo bwihuse, icyorezo cya nyuma n'ubwinshi bwacyo biracyari bitaramenyekana.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 barimo abantu 4,021 banduye COVID-19 ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, bwatanze igishushanyo mbonera cy'icyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
