Igitekerezo cy'uko RNA ifite ubwandu igenda mu ngirabuzimafatizo cyasohoka; nyuma yo gukora kopi y'ubwandu bw'umugera, RNA ya jenomike igenda mu bice by'umubiri bigizwe n'ibinyabuzima birimo glicoprotein n'ibinyabuzima bya nucleocapside, bigakurikiraho gufatanya na membrane ya plasma kugira ngo igende mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
