Ariko kandi, poroteyine za S za SARS-CoV-2 zihuriza ku bantu ACE2 nabi kurusha za S za SARS-CoV, bigatuma SARS-CoV-2 idakira cyane kurusha SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine ntoya nshya, ihinduwe na orf3b, kandi poroteyine ihinduwe ihinduwe na orf8.
Orf3b ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare mu gusohoza ingirabuzima fatizo zandura kandi igahagarika kugaragaza IFNß; nyamara, orf8 nta hantu na hamwe hazwi ho gukora cyangwa intego.
Ku itariki ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al. batangaje ko imiterere ya cryo-EM y'umuntu ufite uburebure bwose bwa ACE2 ku ivangura rya 2.9 Å, yahindutse imiterere ya B0AT1 ikorana na amino acid.
Basanze ingano z'ibinyabuzima by'uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima byari byuguruye n'ibyari byarahagaze, byakoraniye hamwe nk'ibinyabuzima, maze ingano ya ACE2-B0AT1 ishobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, zitanga ibimenyetso byo kumenya ko CoV ifite ubwandu.
