Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri mu 2019, bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abarwaye indwara z'uburwayi bari bafite ari 98%, ubukonje bw'ubushyuhe 76%, dispenia 55% na diariya 3%; abagera kuri 8% babaga bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
