Mu buryo buhuje n'uko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012 ku baturage, abarwayi ba MERS-CoV na bo bagaragaje ko bafite umuriro (98%), ubukana (47%) na dispenia (55%) mu buryo bw'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi.
