Mu byo Leta yatangaje mu ntangiriro harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, kuziba za kaminuza, ibigo by'uburezi bukuru n'amashuri.
Iran yatanze miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'amanyamerika mu kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani, ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020, yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato ibice byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo, ahubwo ko abantu bonyine bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Nubwo hari gahunda zo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi, ingendo nyinshi hagati y'imijyi zakomeje kugera nyuma y'Umwaka mushya w'u Buperesi.
Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, ahantu hatagatifu h'imitako y'aba Shia i Kom, hafunguriwe abapadiri.
Mu gihe cy'ibyifuzo byo guhishura icyorezo cyabaye muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byasubiye inyuma byemeza ko byamaze kugera muri Irani kugeza ku wa 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko icyorezo cyagaragaye ari kinini cyane kurusha icyorezo cya 388 cyabayeho kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe ku wa 3 Werurwe, kubera ko 23 mu 290 bayigize bagaragaje ko bafite virusi y'umugera wa Corona.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza ba Irani kurekura abantu bose bafashe mu maboko yabo bazira ko bahemutse ku burenganzira bwa muntu, kandi ikabategeka kurekura imfungwa zikwiriye.
Yavuze kandi ko mu bigo by'imbohe nk'ibigo by'ubucamanza, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije, hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, guverinoma ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari umubare munini cyane mu gihugu kuva icyo cyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 b'Abanyirani cyangwa abahoze aribo, ndetse n'abayobozi ba Leta, barapfuye.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Coronavirus yari imaze guhitana abantu bashya 50 buri saha, n'urupfu rumwe buri minota 10.
Umukozi wa WHO yavuze ko mu gihugu cya Iran hashobora kuba hari abantu barenga inshuro eshanu ku baregwa.
Hari kandi inama z'uko ibyo Amerika itegeka Irani bigomba kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'icyo gihugu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Umukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku Burenganzira bw'Ikiremwamuntu yasabye ko imishyikirano y'ubukungu ifatwa n'ibindi bihugu, harimo na Iran, yahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye z'icyorezo.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 cyemejwe mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama ubwo abashinwa babiri bageragezwaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Kubera ko umubare w'abanduye wiyongeraga cyane, leta y'u Butaliyani yagombaga guhagarika ingendo zose z'indege ziva mu Bushinwa zigana mu Bushinwa, ndetse n'itegeko ry'imimerere y'ubutagondwa.
Mu mujyi wa Lombardy, ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, habonetse icyorezo cya COVID-19 kitagira aho gihuriye n'ibindi 16 byemejwe. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo guhagarika icyorezo, ryarimo gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu migi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Ahantu hatemba nta muntu uzinjira cyangwa ngo ave".
Hari amabwiriza yo guhagarika ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino muri ako gace. "Ku wa 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifungwa burundu kubera abantu 100 bapfuye mu Butaliyani".
Imikino yose y'imikino ikomeye, harimo imikino ya Serie A, yari kuba mu kibuga gifunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe imikino yose yahagaritswe nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku wa 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Kante yategetse ko ibigo by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bivaho, ndetse n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi, ku wa 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Abitaliyani ryita ku buvuzi, ku buvuzi, ku gutabaza no kugabanya ubushobozi (SIAARTI) ryashyize ahagaragara amahame y'ubuvuzi agaragaza uko umuntu yakwitwara mu gihe ahanganye n'ikibazo cy'ubuvuzi.
Ku wa 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwarushije Ubushinwa mu bihugu byinshi ku isi, bufata iya mbere mu guhitana abantu benshi cyane ku isi kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus, aho bwageze ku bantu 3405 bapfuye.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko indege icyenda z'ingabo z'Uburusiya zoherejwe mu Butaliyani zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwemezwa kugeza ku itariki ya 5 Mata, abantu 158,877 barapfuye, abandi 2,8115 barakira, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN igaragaza ko umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru bo mu Butaliyani ndetse n'abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu, batagira ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bishobora gutuma habaho urupfu rwinshi.
Igisubizo cy'u Bwongereza kuri virusi cyagaragaraga ko ari cyo cyoroheje kurusha ibindi bihugu byanduye, kandi kugeza ku wa 18 Werurwe 2020, guverinoma y'u Bwongereza ntiyari yigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abaturage cyangwa kwihererana n'abaturage.
Ibi byatumye Leta idatangazwa ko itita ku buryo ihita igaragaza uko igenda igaragaza ibibazo abantu bahura na byo. Ku wa 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje itangazo, agasaba abantu kwirinda ingendo n'imishyikirano yose idakenewe, abantu gukora imirimo yo mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka, no kwirinda ahantu nk'aho baba, barya, bakina, n'ibiganiro.
Ku wa 20 Werurwe, Guverinoma yatangaje ko ahantu hose ho gusangira n'abantu, urugero nk'ibigo by'imikino n'imyidagaduro, hagomba gufungwa vuba na bwangu, kandi ko igomba gutanga 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi ku kwezi, ugera ku gipimo cya £2,500, kugira ngo ibikorwa by'ubushomeri birinde mu bihe by'amakuba. Ku wa 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo guhagarika abantu benshi guhurira hamwe, guhagarika ingendo n'imirimo yo hanze, ndetse no kugabanya ibyo basabwa gusa.
Ibyo byari bitandukanye n'ibyo byari bisanzwe, kuko byashoboraga gutuma abapolisi bahabwa ibihano kandi abantu bakava mu ngo zabo.
Ibigo byinshi byategetswe gufungwa, uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi byiswe "ibikenewe cyane" birimo amasupamaketi, ibigo by'ubuvuzi, ibigo by'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga, ibyumba by'ibitoro, ibyumba by'amavuta n'amagaraje.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere cyemejwe ku wa 20 Mutarama muri Leta ya Pacific Northwest, Washington, mu muntu wongeye kugaruka avuye i Wuhan ku wa 15 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama, hashyizweho itsinda ry'abafasha kurwanya Coronavirus mu rugo rwa White House.
Ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari imimerere y'ubuzima bw'abaturage, buhagarika abagenzi bavuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku wa 28 Mutarama 2020, ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ari cyo kigo gishinzwe ubuzima rusange cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byo gupima.
Nyamara, umubare w'ibipimo by'ubwandu muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika wari hasi cyane, ku buryo ubugari nyakuri bw'icyo cyorezo bwari butaramenyekana.
Ibipimo byaranze kubera ibikoresho by'igerageza byakozwe na Leta y'Ubumwe muri Gashyantare, ibikoresho by'igerageza bitari ibya Leta (bitangwa n'amashuri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) byanze kwemerwa na Leta y'Ubumwe kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, kandi abantu bakaba bari bafite ibisabwa by'ibanze kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe kugirango bemererwe kugeragezwa (nyuma yaho bikaba ngombwa ko hakenerwa itegeko ry'abaganga).
Kugeza ku itariki ya 27 Mutarama, Washington Post yatangaje ko nta bigeragezo 4000 byakozwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, Atlantic yatangaje ko nta mashusho 14,000 y'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko abantu bafite ibimenyetso byinshi n'amabwiriza yo kujya kwa muganga, byatwara amasaha n'iminsi kugira ngo bageragezwe. Igihe urupfu rwa mbere rwabaga muri Amerika rwatangiriye i Washington ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Insley yatangaje ko leta yari mu bihe by'ubukene, igikorwa cyakurikiwe n'indi leta.
Amashuri yo mu gace ka Seattle yahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, ndetse amashuri yo mu gihugu hose akaba yarafunze mu kwezi kwa gatatu. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'indwara zo mu rwego rw'icyorezo zo muri Imperial College London zafashije Amerika kumenya uko iyi virusi nshya ya Corona ishobora kugira ingaruka ku gihugu mu gihe kizaza.
Kuri uyu munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'ikoranabuhanga rivuga ko Coronavirus Preparedness and Response Supplemental Approaches Act, riha amafaranga 8.3 y'ubukungu inzego za Leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika kugira ngo zite ku cyorezo.
Ibigo by'ubucuruzi byashyizeho ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo z'abakozi, byasenye inama z'ubuyobozi, kandi byashishikarije abakozi gukora kuva mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'imikino byahagaritswe. Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari iminsi 30 yo guhagarika ingendo zo kuva mu Bwongereza kugera mu Burayi bwose, kuva ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, byongeyeho ko byongeraga amategeko y'ubumwe bw'u Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko hari ibihe by'ubukene mu gihugu, bituma haboneka amafaranga y'ubushami yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu tariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibikorwa byinshi byo mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi byahagaritswe cyangwa amasaha y'akazi yagabanutse muri Amerika.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, byemejwe ko mu bihugu 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia, abantu bose bari banduye Coronavirus bari mu mujyi wa New York, ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko mu mujyi wa New York hari abantu 10.700 banduye Coronavirus, bakaba bari benshi cyane kurusha abanduye bose muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku wa 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko kuboneza urubyaro mu baturage bigaragara ko bihindura ibintu, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanyijwe igera ku minsi 4.7, kuva ku minsi 2.0 kugeza ku minsi 4.7.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, mu mujyi wa New York hari abantu 32308 banduye, abantu 672 bahitanwe na virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zavuze ko hari abantu benshi banduye virusi ya Corona kurusha ikindi gihugu cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari abantu 400,335 banduye, abantu 12841 bapfuye.
Amakuru yo ku wa 30 Werurwe avuga ko Perezida wa Amerika Trump yongereyeho amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwa USS Comfort bwari bufite ibitaro 1000 bwarashyize ubwato i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, muri Amerika habaye umubare munini w'abapfuye baguye muri iki cyorezo, bagera ku 884 mu masaha 24.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, umubare w'abanduye muri Leta ya New York warenze 100.000, kubera ko White House yanenze cyane ko yagabanyije uburemere bw'akaga, kandi ko yagabanyije ubufatanye bwa Mike Pence, Visi Perezida, mu gutanga itangazo n'ibitangazamakuru ku bantu bose ku byerekeye iyi virusi, binyuze mu kugenzura ubutumwa bwatanzwe n'abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga.
Muri rusange, uburyo ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwemeye iki kibazo bwari bwarashyize hamwe kandi bufite aho bugarukira.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi banenze ko Amerika yari ikomeje kwishingikiriza ku kwinjiza ibintu by'ingenzi mu Bushinwa, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ingenzi.
Ibisobanuro by'ibipimo by'indege byakoreshejwe mu gukora igitabo cy'ibanze cy'ibyerekeye ingendo n'ibyerekeye ingendo, byasohotse mu kinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi bw'ingendo mu kwezi kwa mbere.
Mu 2018, International Air Transport Association (IATA) yavuze ko abagenzi benshi bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan bajya i Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ari bo bari benshi.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu hazwi cyane ku bantu bajya gutembera i Wuhan.
Mu bihugu 20 by'ingenzi, Bali ni cyo cya mbere mu bihugu by'ibihangange mu guhangana n'icyorezo, naho mu mijyi ya Autriche ni ho by'ingenzi cyane.
Yavuze ko hari ubushakashatsi bwinshi bukomeje gukorwa kuri COVID-19 kandi ko Australia izakomeza gushimangira uko ikora ku mipaka yo ku mugabane w'isi.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, Australia yatangaje ibihe by'ubukene bw'ikirere.
Kubera ko gahunda yo gutwara abantu benshi mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uwa Hubei yagabanyijwe mu buryo bugaragara, ibihugu byinshi biteganya gutwara abaturage babyo n'abakozi bo hanze y'igihugu, cyane cyane ku ndege z'igihugu cyabo, kandi byemejwe n'abayobozi b'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Arjantina, Ubudage na Thailand ni byo bihugu bya mbere byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazatuma abaturage bayo bava mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brazil yafashe abantu bane bo muri Polonye, umuntu umwe wo mu Bushinwa n'undi muntu wo mu Buhinde, hamwe n'abantu 34 bo muri Brazil cyangwa imiryango yabo.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde bahageze muri Polonye aho indege ya Brazil yari yahagaze mbere yo kujya muri Brazil.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari bagiye i Wuhan, bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi y'igihugu cya Brazil.
Kuri uwo munsi, abaturage 215 bo muri Canada (ku ndege ya mbere 176 n'indi ya kabiri ya leta ya Amerika 39), bavuye i Wuhan bajya muri CFB Trenton mu cyiciro cya kabiri cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Indi ndege ya CFB yabashije kugera i Trenton ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, yari ivuye i Wuhan igeze ku baturage 185 bo muri Canada.
Abayobozi ba Australia bafashe abaturage 277 bajya mu kigo cy'i Kikirisimasi Island cyo ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, cyongeye gushyirwa mu kato, aho bari bamaze iminsi 14.
Igihe indege y'abimukira bo muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageraga i Auckland ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, abagenzi bari bayirimo (bari bamwe mu baturage bo muri Australia no muri Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'ingabo z'abasirikare i Wangaparoua, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zari kuzashyikiriza abaturage ba Amerika bari ku bwato bwa Diamond Express.
Indege yari ivuye muri Diamond Princess ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, yari ihagaritse urugendo rw'abashyitsi 129 bo muri Canada, ihaguruka i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, Guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye guhunga abaturage bayo bava muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yemewe na Guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yafashe abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Mbere yo kugenda, abaganga bagerageje kugenzura abarwayi bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'icyorezo cya Coronavirusi, kugira ngo birinde ibyago.
Abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bonyine bagaragaye ko badakora neza, ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu bihugu byabo.
Ibizamini by'imyanzuro byatanze igihamya cy'uko abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi b'indege, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari muri iki gikorwa cy'ubutabazi, bari baraye muri The Ranch Resort mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 y'irengagizwa ry'abantu, barekuwe.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane cyatumye Amerika itangira gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraq mu buryo bwuzuye.
Ku wa 5 Gashyantare, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (birimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byoherereje ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi Ubushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri za kaminuza za Amerika bafatanyije n'itsinda ry'abashyize hamwe bo mu mujyi wa Chicago mu Bushinwa, kugira ngo bohereze ubufasha mu gace gashyirwamo virusi muri icyo gihugu, iryo tsinda ryavugaga ko ku wa 30 Mutarama ryagiye riyobora kohereza ama mask 50000 N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku mikoro n'imihati yo kuvura abantu bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Interaksioni yatangaje ko ku wa 6 Gashyantare, leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze amasikuru ibihumbi 2000 ku baturage ba Philippines nyuma y'uko umunyamuryango wa Sena Richard Gordonney yoherereje Wuhan amasikuru miliyoni 3.16.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Red Crown ya Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amafaranga yo gufasha u Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze amasiki y'uruhu miliyoni imwe mu mpano, u Turukiya bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwatanze toni zisaga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Busuwisi bwatangaje ko bwatanze miliyoni 18 z'amakanzu y'ubuvuzi ku Bushinwa, u Budage bwatanze toni 1000 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda yo kwirinda akaga, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zitanga toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi ku Bushinwa, kandi zizeza ko izindi miriyoni 100 z'amadolari zizashyikirizwa ibihugu bifite ibibazo by'ubukungu.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus mu Butaliyani.
Umukozi w'ubucuruzi Jack Ma yoherereje Addis Ababa Ethiopia ibikoresho by'imibonano mpuzabitsina miliyoni 1.1 n'amasiki y'amaso miliyoni 6 n'imyenda 60000 y'ubwirinzi, byatanzwe n'umuryango w'ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yaho yohereje ibipimo 5000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 1000 n'imiti itanu yo guhumeka muri Panama.
Ma na we yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. U Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatanze impungenge ku masiki n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho 58000 by'igeragezwa ry'umugera wa Corona byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite igipimo cyo kwizigamira ku kigero cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwasabye amasiki y'amaso 600,000 y'Ubushinwa yari afite ubumuga.
Ububiligi bwasabye abantu 10.000 gusubiza udupfukamunwa tudakwiriye gukoresha twasaga n'aho twavuye mu Bushinwa ariko mu by'ukuri tukava muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza muri Amerika y'Epfo no muri Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangiye ibikorwa byo guhita itanga inkunga ku bihugu byateye imbere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) rishimiye ingamba z'abayobozi b'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
OMS yatangaje itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo hagati ya 2002-2004 ubwo abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryatumye imihati yo gukumira iki cyorezo igenda itandukana no kwirinda iki cyorezo, n'ikibazo cy'iki gihe aho leta y'u Bushinwa yatanze amakuru ajyanye n'iki cyorezo mu rwego rwo kwirinda guhungabana mu gihe cy'Umwaka mushya w'Umwezi.
Mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'abayobozi b'u Burayi cyo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 23 Mutarama, uhagarariye WHO, Goden Geli, yavuze ko inama ya WHO atari yo, kandi ko igaragaza ko abantu bagomba gufatirwa hamwe mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'indwara ya Sida, aho cyakomeje kwiyongera, ndetse ko ari "ikintu kitigeze kiba mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange".
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, Tedros Ahanom, yavuze ko PHIC ibitewe n'akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abari mu kigero cy'abari mu nzego z'ubuzima, aho gahunda z'ubuzima zitagikora.
Mu gusubiza ku bihano ku rugendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zidafite ishingiro zituma habaho ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga" kandi ko "WHO idashyigikira ibihano ku bucuruzi n'imikorere".
