Nubwo ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bitagaragara ko bifite akamaro kanini kurusha ibikoresho by'ubuhanga n'ubuyobozi, bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda zimwe mu ndwara.
Buri bwoko bwa PPE bugomba guhitamo bitewe n'akaga kabwo, bukwiye kuba buhuye neza n'uko ikoreshwa (urugero, respirateurs) kandi bukambara neza, bukagenzurwa buri gihe, bukomeze kubungabunga kandi bukongorwa uko bikenewe, bukongorwa neza, bukomeze guturwa neza, bukomeze kubungabunga cyangwa bukongorwa neza kugira ngo buveho icyorezo.
Dukurikije ubuyobozi bwa Amerika bw'umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi (OSHO), imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura byoroheje cyane, igaragaza ko igomba kugirana n'abantu benshi n'abandi bakozi imishyikirano yoroheje.
Gufata ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura mu kazi kose birasabwa, harimo gukaraba intoki no kuzisukura, guhamagarira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo guhumeka, harimo no guhosha no gukubita akanwa igihe baguye, gutanga imbaho zo gukorora impapuro n'ibisigazwa, gutegura itumanaho cyangwa imirimo y'ubushomeri iyo bibaye ngombwa, guhashya abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gusukura no guhumanya ahantu ho gukora imirimo buri gihe.
Kwihutira kumenya abantu bashobora kuba banduye no kubashyira mu kato ni intambwe ikomeye mu gutuma abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi barindwa mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama ko abakozi bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu guhumeka, bagomba kuguma mu rugo nibura amasaha 24 bataragize umuriro, ibimenyetso by'ubushyuhe n'ibindi bimenyetso, kandi ko hari gahunda y'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara ihinduka, ituma abakozi baba mu rugo kugira ngo bita ku muntu urwaye mu muryango wabo, kandi ko abakozi bazi iyo politiki.
OSHA ivuga ko imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura hagati harimo gukora akazi k'abantu bataramenyekana cyangwa badafite ibimenyetso by'uko banduye COVID-19, ariko bakaba bakomeje gukwirakwiza mu gace k'ubucuruzi cyangwa bakaba baherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga aho COVID-19 ikwirakwira cyane, bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2, bityo bakaba bagomba kuba bari hafi y'abantu bagera kuri metero esheshatu (1.8m) z'uruhu.
Muri ibi harimo abakozi bagirana na rubanda rusangi imishyikirano, nk'amashuri, ahantu h'akazi hatuwe n'abaturage benshi ndetse na bimwe mu bigo bikomeye by'ubucuruzi. Ingingo z'ubugenzuzi zigamije guhangana n'ibibazo by'uburwayi ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi, harimo gushyiraho filtre z'umwuka z'ingirakamaro cyane ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi, kongera umubare w'ibikinisho by'umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'urinda imyanda ya plastiki ihenze, no gushyiraho idirishya ry'umwunganira ry'abakozi.
Abakozi bo muri iyi nzego z'ibyago ntibakunze gukenera gukoresha respiratori.
Mu gihe umuntu arwaye mu ndege, kugenzura neza kugira ngo arinde abakozi n'abandi bantu, birimo kumugenera ahantu ha metero 6 kuva ku bandi, gushyiraho umwe mu bagize itsinda ry'abasirikare bafasha uwo muntu urwaye, no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba guhita yikorera akanwa n'akanwa mu gihe avuza cyangwa avuza.
Iyo ukorera umurwayi cyangwa ukageraho ukagera ku mazi y'umubiri we cyangwa ku gice cyanduye, ugomba kwambara imyenda y'ubuvuzi ikoreshwa mu kuvura, kandi iyo umurwayi arwaye indwara y'umuriro, guhora ashonja cyangwa guhumeka nabi, ugomba kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'ibanze by'umuntu ku giti cye.
Gufata ingofero n'ibindi bintu bicyekwa bisaba ko bicyekwa mu mufuka w'amaboko, hanyuma bikayisukura kandi bigasenya ahantu habanduye. Ku mato y'ingendo n'andi mato y'ingenzi, harimo n'amato y'ingendo, kugenzura ibyago bikubiyemo guhagarika urugendo igihe urwaye no kwihagarika mu gihe uri ku bwato, mu gihe ufite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso, no guhita ubimenyesha ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cyo ku bwato.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, icyumba cy'umuntu uherereye mu rugo gikwiye gukurikiranwa n'abaganga. CDC itera inkunga ko umuntu urwaye iyo abonye mu mashuri no mu bigo by'abana, yaba akwirakwira mu muryango cyangwa atabikora, agomba gufungwa by'agateganyo kugira ngo ashobore gukora isuku no kwitsemamo.
Aho haba hari ugukwirakwira kw'abaturage ku rugero ruto, hari uburyo bwo gushyiraho amabwiriza y'ubutabazi, urugero nko gukora ingendo zo mu murima, guhagarika ibirori bikomeye birimo kwigisha abantu benshi no gukora imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa gusangira mu mashuri yo gusenga cyangwa mu mahoteli, kongera amabanga hagati y'amazu yo gusangira, guhindura amasaha yo kuza no kugenda, kugabanya abaza batazi icyo bakora, no gushyiraho ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwihariye ku bana bafite ibimenyetso nk'icyorezo cy'indwara.
Mu gihe hari ubwandu bukomeye mu itsinda ry'abaturage, harimo n'ingamba zo kwirinda kubana n'abandi, amashuri ashobora gufungwa igihe kirekire.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko basabwa guhuza n'abandi bantu banduye COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura, bagirwa inama yo gukurikiza amabwiriza hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye, kimwe n'abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi b'ubutabazi.
Iyo habayeho guhura na hafi mu gihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'itumanaho, abakozi bagomba gukora isuku no guhumeka bakoresheje imvururu cyangwa imyenda yo mu rugo mbere yo kongera gukoresha imyenda n'ibikoresho byabo, kandi bagakurikiza uburyo busanzwe bwo kuvanaho PPE ikoreshwa, kubika imyenda itandukanye no gukaraba, mu gihe cy'igihe gito kigenwe.
